#######
#ingame
#######

^#5aa9d6;All vanilla clothing options available for all vanilla races in character creation. Hilarity ensues.^reset;

This mod will lead to some absolutely ridiculous combinations. Not recomended for generation of a world that you are planning on taking seriously.

Now properly extends these changes to generated villagers.

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

######
#steam
######

[h1]All vanilla clothing options available for all vanilla races in character creation. Hilarity ensues.[/h1]
This mod will lead to some absolutely ridiculous combinations. Not recomended for generation of a world that you are planning on taking seriously.
Now properly extends these changes to generated villagers.

